<refsect1 id="harfbuzz-hb-ot-font.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>Functions for using OpenType fonts with <link linkend="hb-shape"><function>hb_shape()</function></link>.  Note that fonts returned
by <link linkend="hb-font-create"><function>hb_font_create()</function></link> default to using these functions, so most clients would
never need to call these functions directly.</para>

</refsect1>
